{"tid":1355602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔正傻鳩，去掃元朗咪中哂計囉！","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:05:44.000Z","uid":54303,"like":10,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4d0119672c55eee0bdfbf66eae23e1f9730cd0","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:38:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔正傻鳩，去掃元朗咪中哂計囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為件事定性錯撚哂呀！<br />\n元朗恐襲係由中聯辦策畫，警察同港鐵默許既罪行。<br />\n入元朗唔係為左掃元朗班垃圾，佢地本身就死不足惜。<br />\n入元朗係為左<span style=\"color: red;\">控訴官商鄉黑，聯手欺壓香港人</span>呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細心諗下有咩人參與呢次恐襲：<br />\n中聯辦（官）：主謀，想用白色恐怖嚇我地，令香港人收聲<br />\n警犬（官）：食花生，因為敵視市民，所以濫權包庇白衫暴徒<br />\n港府（官）：食花生，<span style=\"color: red;\">連宣布暴動都唔撚肯</span>，弱智<br />\n商（港鐵）：引清兵入關，完全無保護乘客，因為政府係大股東<br />\n白衫畜牲（鄉、黑）出力，唔洗多講，全部都要落地獄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔該各位文宣上做到「對準政權」，大力聲討官商鄉黑（尤其係警黑勾結，直接造成恐襲）。希望遊行果時唔會見到d標語淨係針對元朗鄉黑，一定要拉埋官商落水。而且呢件事要大力對外宣傳，務求醜事傳千里。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宣傳做錯，大獲過意外燒死一兩隻畜牲。畜牲無人同情，但我地唔可以降到佢地既層次去發洩。所以<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要堅守五大訴求，持續對準政權。</span><br />\n係咁多。"},{"pid":"a439bfc121bc4465a311fe78ff4e76df96097d51","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90308ef9e79cf700e841f660cdb5799a10ac7d15","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97348a22f0ebbf9bfdb0cb375e75b15af9f131ed","tid":1355602,"uid":15341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n不要中計"},{"pid":"07f8ffebb720884a89fba54488abe2d0d5fc1b32","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"054ea9b4958a103480451f597b1455fa8338871e","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd7c36223d6621f25c7960ee1473490ce9d18d8e","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c08687731ac5b5c7c77772af634fa6ac0b5f8fc5","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ace8ecf324e83b549efa10a16f061bded105d783","tid":1355602,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"推，搵返焦點"},{"pid":"bf3f6d7ab07c6c30dfc1e3d5e7ece23b82573a90","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:15:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e497ed6cd85446266fc02bcb117e87e99f62007","tid":1355602,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政黑同流<br />\n警黑合汚</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"82a1a12a55377833ab1d8b50abce00de975c56ae","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bce49225eac75f715510c4af4b8771bd2bbdfc7","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"feeae9f165bcab04b68439f02ca1079ad18acc40","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:02:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27413b849fd25737d8cab52f145525d482095155","tid":1355602,"uid":234525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"「中晒計啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8d7384a5036ca622b1d7e3e0dfd59bb6d0ff33","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:05:21.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9a589098c59028e919cd8414d03e22ebcb7dce25","tid":1355602,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2